summary: Adds many new factors to the Jorrvaskr area in Whiterun. This mod improves the forge, exterior decor, adds a travel marker, improved interior, improved underforge (slightly), and adds a lost home beneath the Underforge.
descriptionHtml:
[center][img] https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-3Lsq2cc22Hc/UNuD6xPiQ7I/AAAAAAAAAik/9pibZfJFcUE/s752/AA03small.jpg [/img][/center]

[center][img]https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-s2qNEDCn4mo/UNzj-pNYEAI/AAAAAAAAAo4/m34KKqctedk/s800/dmcline.png[/img][/center]

[quote] [i]\"Hey, Thanks! I love Jorrvaskr\'s new look! It used to be trashy, but now... Beautiful.\" - [MQ] Vinyl-Scratch-Dj-P0n-3 from Steam Workshop [/i] [/quote]

[img=center] https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-e89xmhpVEZ4/UNuR75MjVqI/AAAAAAAAAjo/N2D-LKkVBtM/s800/Untitled01.png [/img]

Better Jorrvaskr provides you with a more colorful approach on your experience fighting alongside the companions. This mod features an improved forge, a massively improved exterior, an improved main hall, an improved living quarters, adds a map marker, adds new followers and merchants residing in Jorrvaskr, and adds a completely new Undercity, equipped with Ante-chambers, and a full new player home.

	The Forge is now equipped with a Tanning Rack, a Weapon Rack, a Workbench, a Smelter, and many pre-made weapons and armor on tables, along with pelts.

	The Exterior is now full with different arrays of floral life, trees and plants, has new benches around Jorrvaskr, Creates new arches in front of Jorrvaskr & the Skyforge, adds a Companion Dog & a Companion Goat, adds many new training dummys, adds many statues around Jorrvaskr, adds a bar on the patio with itâ€™s own bartender, and many more new features!

	The Main Hall now has a redone table, instead of having food catered to the Companions, now they have empty plates, and have to fetch their own food & mead, it also adds a Grindstone, a Workbench, a Bard, Bookshelves & display plaques, and much more.

	If you would like to learn more, download it for yourself!

[line]

[img] https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-U2JCg-S701M/UNuTE36YBCI/AAAAAAAAAkA/Zq3Qf1EwYsw/s800/Untitled03.png [/img]

[heading][color=#FFD564]V.1 (Version 1) Includes:[/color][/heading]
[list]
[*] Improved Forge (Tanning Rack, Pelts, Workbench)
[*] New Mage Companion Follower
[*] Better Exterior
[*] Jorrvaskr Patio includes Alchemy Table and Enchanting Table
[*] New Dining Table Interior, includes Cooking Spit above fire
[*] New Chests, New Ancient Companion Weapons
[/list]

[heading][color=#FFD564]V.1.5 (Version 1.5) Includes:[/color][/heading]
[list]
[*] All of the above
[*] Read Me doc
[*] All Screenshots
[*] Few New Weapons
[/list]

[heading][color=#FFD564]V 2.0 (Version 2.0) Includes:[/color][/heading]
[list]
[*] New Jorrvaskr Map Location
[*] New Dovahkiin Living Area
[*] Large amount of Exterior Decor
[*] New Restoration Spell
[*] New Weapons and Armor
[*] New Hidden Room
[*] New Bar
[*] New Followers
[*] New Merchant\'s
[/list]

[heading][color=#FFD564]V2.5 (Version 2.5) Includes:[/color][/heading]
[list]
[*] New Jorrvaskr Catacomb Room.
[*] Companion Dog
[/list]

[heading][color=#FFD564]V3.0 (Version 3.0) Includes:[/color][/heading]
[list]
[*] General Cleanup
[*] Generic Improvements
[*] Companion Shield
[/list]

[heading][color=#FFD564]V3.5 (Version 3.5) TES5Edit:[/color][/heading]
[list]
[*] TES5Edit Cleanup
[/list]

[heading][color=#FFD564]V4.0 (Version 4.0) Includes:[/color][/heading]
[list]
[*] Cleanup
[*] Tidyness
[*] Better Patio
[*] Better Player Quarters
[*] More Plants & Trees
[/list]

[heading][color=#FFD564]V5.0 (Version 5.0) Includes:[/color][/heading]
[list]
[*] More Organized Patio
[*] Improved Forge Area
[*] Slightly Improved Living Quarters
[*] Completely Re-done Jorrvaskr Undercity (Accessible through Underforge) (***ONLY OBTAINED THROUGH COMPANION QUEST COMPLETION! If you wish to enter early, open the command window and enter \"coc whiterununderforge\" ***)
[/list]

[heading][color=#FFD564]V5.5 (Version 5.5) Includes:[/color][/heading]
[list]
[*] Finished, Improved, and Cleaned All Underground Units (Jorrvaskr Undercity) (INCLUDES PLAYER HOME)
[/list]

[heading][color=#FFD564]V6.0 (Version 6.0) Includes:[/color][/heading]
[list]
[*] Improved Main Jorrvaskr
[*] Improved Living Quarters
[*] Improved Key Obtainment
[*] Vastly Improved Undercity
[*] All New Weapons!!! From JaySus Swords Mod
[/list]

[heading][color=#FFD564]V6.5 (Version 6.5) Includes: [/color][/heading]
[list]
[*] Improved Undercity
[/list]

[heading][color=#FFD564]V7.0 (Version 7.0) Includes: [/color][/heading]
[list]
[*] Improved Undercity
[*] Improved Main Table
[/list]

[heading][color=#FFD564]V8.0 (Version 8.0) Includes: [/color][/heading]
[list]
[*] Improved Player Home
[*] Improved Lighting/FX Effects
[/list]

[heading][color=#FFD564]V9.0 (Version 9.0) Includes: [/color][/heading]
[list]
[*] All New Cells Navmeshed, except main Home, coming navmeshed in next update.
[*] Altered Armors of NPCs
[*] Altered Faces, Warpaint, Hair, ETC
[*] Tweaked Exterior
[/list]

[heading][color=#FFD564]V10.0 (Version 10.0) (FINAL UPDATE) Includes:[/color][/heading]
[list]
[*] Minor Updates
[*] File Archive Added
[*] NOTE: For those of you who actually read this and are disappointed that I\'m archiving this project and not adding any more updates, I am creating a mod similar to Jorrvaskr, a sort of Companion sanctuary, It will require Dawnguard since the Hall will be based on the Dawnguard Fort files. It will be based in a snow filled area, such as Dawnstar or Windhelm. More details to come, I will include a link when it\'s done. I hope you enjoy Better Jorrvaskr, and it\'s been a pleasure having you guys support me in this project.
[/list]
